item.description:
Ted will set up a netsat around 5:30 PM; I'll be there at 6:00 PM.

Location: Grass fields at Sidney and Pacific Street in Cambridge.

Access by T: Central Square stop. Walk down Mass Ave towards MIT and make a right on Sidney Street (There's a restaurant called Asgard on the corner of Sidney Street). Walk down Sidney street about 4 blocks to Pacific Street. It's about a 5-10 minute walk from the T stop.

Parking: There are meter spots on the street that are free to park at after 6 PM.
item.name: Cambridge volleyball Wed 9/24 @ 5:30 PM
